    "description": "<strong>决策与策略</strong><br>每回合进行选择，获取新单位，还是扩展地图，亦或是获取新增益效果；<br>如何排布单位放置，让各个单位都能更好收益而不是互相造成负面影响；<br><br><strong>肉鸽要素</strong><br>四大类单位，矮人，设备，植物，动物，各有其单位特色和注重的产出影响方向，还有在高难度下出现的灾难单位，会产生可规避的负面影响；<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/3423d71ef4be85fee0930c8bd0fffa91.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/118e4492f1f2c2dd7db3dc9516d0f74f.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/02127cd814786935426ca12a71ea3e3f.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/13efc1084a1118d9c325e74abe889ddf.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>不同的增益，这些特殊的全局buff会提供大量金币，围绕所选增益来选择不同的单位：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/71086490facaf72985e1a2bcb8f19fde.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/29787841e023c3b4e530cf423c8f0869.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/ea6c61e350cdf4c259abf4c00c57fa0b.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/a1a72c113b22f32a6c569ca8ba3a8231.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <br><br><strong>简明的游戏目标</strong><br>你只需要关注一个目标，那就是获得超过目标金额的金币，策略性的放置单位来实现这一点，希望你能享受思考的过程。",
